2
00:00:12.384 --> 00:00:14.870
<v ->One of the real enigmas within the history of science</v>

3
00:00:14.870 --> 00:00:18.038
is that the original members of the British Royal Society,

4
00:00:18.038 --> 00:00:20.075
men such as Isaac Newton,

5
00:00:20.075 --> 00:00:22.705
were what author Peter Taylor calls alchemists,

6
00:00:22.705 --> 00:00:25.345
who possessed highly refined levels of knowledge.

7
00:00:25.345 --> 00:00:28.369
Rather than imparting this knowledge to the masses, however,

8
00:00:28.369 --> 00:00:30.022
they gave birth to what we know

9
00:00:30.022 --> 00:00:31.836
today as the traditional sciences,

10
