16
00:01:00.699 --> 00:01:03.435
and she said, "No, we haven't gotten into the subject

17
00:01:03.435 --> 00:01:06.843
"of alchemy and how this eventually

18
00:01:06.843 --> 00:01:08.545
"gave way to modern science."

