00:01:08.545 --> 00:01:10.849
I thought, whoopee, let's just pick our conversation

20
00:01:10.849 --> 00:01:14.007
up with Peter at this point, because I think

21
00:01:14.007 --> 00:01:16.599
it's almost a continued conversation that way.

22
00:01:16.599 --> 00:01:20.823
So we had had an off-camera conversation about this before

23
00:01:20.823 --> 00:01:23.991
and I thought this is a direction I'd like to go,

24
00:01:23.991 --> 00:01:26.919
which is going back to the Royal Society

25
00:01:26.919 --> 00:01:29.129
and some of the most famous names in,

26
