quote, modern science, including Newton,

27
00:01:33.017 --> 00:01:34.927
and I would like you to reveal to us

28
00:01:34.927 --> 00:01:37.423
what you have put together regarding this story

29
00:01:37.423 --> 00:01:41.023
of how these alchemists essentially foisted modern science

30
00:01:41.023 --> 00:01:43.903
upon the rest of us which is so incredibly restrictive.

31
00:01:43.903 --> 00:01:46.554
<v ->It's a very recent conclusion,</v>

32
00:01:46.554 --> 00:01:48.810
that that's what's happened.

