00:01:48.810 --> 00:01:51.280
First of all, I didn't know that

34
00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:53.395
the founders of the Royal Society

35
00:01:53.395 --> 00:01:57.131
were essentially what we would call magicians.

36
00:01:57.131 --> 00:01:59.473
I didn't even know what alchemists were.

37
