00:03:30.664 --> 00:03:35.270
was his alchemical partner in this inner journey.

64
00:03:35.270 --> 00:03:38.339
And that, within the biography,

65
00:03:38.339 --> 00:03:40.700
Elias Ashmolean joins

66
00:03:40.700 --> 00:03:44.729
with several other alchemists

