00:08:50.673 --> 00:08:53.445
into cities,

166
00:08:53.445 --> 00:08:56.805
and into jobs, and into industry,

167
00:08:56.805 --> 00:09:01.509
which, almost in any definition, would be soul destroying,

168
00:09:02.789 --> 00:09:06.719
that they lose so much in that transition,

169
00:09:06.719 --> 00:09:11.543
and I'll give them then money in exchange,

170
00:09:11.543 --> 00:09:15.305
they become wage slaves.

171
00:09:15.305 --> 00:09:17.033
<v Regina>Well, this is where we are today.</v>

